Cancer Weekly Horoscope
Your leisure and pleasure sector encourages you to let your creative muse out to play. Indeed, indulging in your favorite hobbies can exorcise your demons while producing some inspiring or intriguing artwork. Don't underestimate the power of such activities to heal and restore your spirits. As Mars dances into your home sector you might need to establish firm boundaries regarding household tasks and everyday chores, especially, if you've been doing most of them until now.